# POLICY: @yingbull must approve ALL changes to protected branches.
# No exceptions. When delegating the * catch-all to others in future,
# every section below still requires @yingbull.
#
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners


